Package: spNetwork
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Analysis on Network
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeremy", "Gelb", email = "jeremy.gelb@ucs.inrs.ca",role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Philippe", "Apparicio", email="philippe.apparicio@ucs.inrs.ca", role=c("ctb")))
Description: The spNetwork package provides functions to perform spatial analysis on network.
    In its actual form, it allows to calculate Network Kernel Density Estimate, and to build
    spatial matrices (listw objects like in 'spdep' package) to perform any kind of traditional 
    spatial analysis with spatial weights based on reticular distances.
